Third chair
at table eight can't lose.

27:59.604 --> 28:02.672
Unless there are players
at his table who can win.

28:02.674 --> 28:05.308
You know about the game
at the Cobra Lounge, right?

28:05.310 --> 28:06.342
Sure.

28:06.344 --> 28:08.778
One thousand for every player
you send me.

28:08.780 --> 28:10.780
You get a piece
