28:30.569 --> 28:31.901
They alone control the market.

28:31.903 --> 28:34.271
They chose the artist
they wanna be important.

28:34.273 --> 28:35.738
They don't mind
spending $10 million

28:35.740 --> 28:37.974
on a pitcher
who is 8-14 this season.

28:37.976 --> 28:39.576
- It's gonna be Gephardt.
- They set the prices.

28:39.578 --> 28:42.479
They even mark 'em up,
70, 80, 90 percent.

28:42.481 --> 28:45.282
They're all very excited
about a company called Twitter.

28:45.284 --> 28:47.617
Unregulated money.
Usually all cash. Unreported.

28:47.619 --> 28:49.418
- His days are numbered.
- His days are numbered.

28:49.420 --> 28:50.786
I don't know how much longer
she's gonna be in that job.

28:50.788 --> 28:51.820
- She's done.
- She's gone.

28:51.822 --> 28:53.255
All in.

28:53.257 --> 28:54.291
<i>People have asked me what</i>

28:54.293 --> 28:55.692
<i>my goal was at that point.</i>

28:55.694 --> 28:57.327
<i>What was my end game?</i>

28:57.329 --> 28:59.862
<i>Back then, I would have
laughed at that question.</i>

28:59.864 --> 29:01.630
<i>I was raised to be a champion.</i>

29:01.632 --> 29:03.166
<i>My goal was to win.</i>

29:03.168 --> 29:04.967
<i>At what and against whom?</i>

29:04.969 --> 29:07.369
- <i>Those were just details.</i>
- I'm all in.

29:07.371 --> 29:08.672
<i>I had my own apartment now.</i>

29:08.674 --> 29:09.805
I'll take it.

29:09.807 --> 29:11.840
<i>A new car...</i>

29:11.842 --> 29:14.109
<i>and $17,000 in a shoebox.</i>

29:14.111 --> 29:16.082
<i>Law school could wait
one more year.</i>

29:18.050 --> 29:21.350
<i>Next, please. Come on through.</i>

29:21.352 --> 29:25.222
<i>Step on up please. Thank you.
Come on through.</i>

29:25.224 --> 29:27.823
So. Here's all that's
gonna happen today.

29:27.825 --> 29:29.259
Judge is gonna ask
each defendant

29:29.261 --> 29:30.560
if they've read the indictment

29:30.562 --> 29:32.795
or they'd like the court
to read it to them.

29:32.797 --> 29:35.130
Then the judge is gonna ask
how you plead.

29:35.132 --> 29:37.167
You're gonna answer,
"Not guilty."

29:37.169 --> 29:38.601
I'll make it clear
for the record

29:38.603 --> 29:39.668
that I'm not your counsel

