01:23:06.774 --> 01:23:09.075
<i>No. There wasn't.</i>

01:23:09.077 --> 01:23:11.114
I'm gonna go all in.

01:24:08.170 --> 01:24:10.637
I wish I had better news.

01:24:10.639 --> 01:24:13.440
Harrison Wellstone didn't go
