help them convict

01:24:34.363 --> 01:24:36.029
the Russians, but you
know things that can help them.

01:24:36.031 --> 01:24:38.498
Did you know that
97 percent of Federal cases

01:24:38.500 --> 01:24:39.732
never make it to trial?

