01:29:14.542 --> 01:29:17.110
<i>wasn't what you would
call... real.</i>

01:29:17.112 --> 01:29:18.745
<i>It was a Ponzi scheme.</i>

01:29:18.747 --> 01:29:20.879
<i>He'd been falsely reporting
