These names were provided
by Brad Marion.

01:30:27.648 --> 01:30:30.083
<i>So, under oath...</i>

01:30:30.085 --> 01:30:33.419
Yes. I can confirm
the list is accurate.

01:30:33.421 --> 01:30:35.888
<i>The L.A. players
and I were given a choice.</i>

