02:05:33.118 --> 02:05:34.584
- It's mine.
- Oh, that's great.

02:05:34.586 --> 02:05:37.154
Well, we don't have
the luxury of integrity.

02:05:37.156 --> 02:05:39.322
- You have to take the deal.
- No.

02:05:39.324 --> 02:05:41.157
