from my personal experience

02:10:00.152 --> 02:10:01.685
trying to spit at it.

02:10:01.687 --> 02:10:03.286
The men and women
who work there will commit

02:10:03.288 --> 02:10:05.388
more serious crimes
by lunchtime today

02:10:05.390 --> 02:10:08.392
