02:11:15.461 --> 02:11:17.361
Make way, people!
Make way!

02:11:17.363 --> 02:11:19.196
Patrol here, move away!
Move away!

02:11:19.198 --> 02:11:21.397
<i>I owe the government
close to $2,000,000</i>

02:11:21.399 --> 02:11:24.200
<i>in taxes assessed
