02:11:24.202 --> 02:11:26.503
<i>Plus, a $200,000 fine.</i>

02:11:26.505 --> 02:11:28.237
<i>And you better believe
they're gonna come get it.</i>

02:11:28.239 --> 02:11:30.874
Clear a path!
